cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.RO 

This paper focuses on improving object detection performance using deep neural networks, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed approach involves data augmentation, which is a common technique in machine learning and deep learning, making cs.LG and cs.AI also likely sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of robotic vision, which falls under cs.RO. Finally, the paper discusses the computational complexity of training deep neural networks, which is a topic in cs.NE.
